text: Folks, Since the vHackfest has been postponed due to vacations and availability, there will be no Arch-WG general session this week. We will resume at our regular scheduled slot on Wed. Aug 31st.
Looks like enough of the documentation sub-team is available for us to review and work-on the Arch Doc draft at 10 AM PDT on Thursday. Will setup and post the Webex for 10 AM PDT on Thursday 25th.
